  "body": "Here is my use case:\n\nAlign component can make its root DOM node align with another node, so Align component need to access other DOM node (for example parent DOM node) on componentDidMount/DidUpdate.\n\nDemo:  http://react-component.github.io/align/examples/simple.html\n\nCurrently I have to hack inside componentDidMount/DidUpdate using setTimeout: https://github.com/react-component/align/blob/4093774c326787830a1b57bd276300b040fc7fe4/src/Align.jsx#L33\n\nOr is there a better way?\n",
